description:
Welcome, Gloss over the stay details 
Type of stay ( ENTIRE 1 BHK)
- 1 BHK Apartment with living room, kitchen, Bedroom with attached bathroom.
Amenities 
- king size bed
- comfortable Sleepwell mattress
- Essentials ( Towels, soaps, Handwash, toilet paper, extra blankets)
- Air Conditioner
- Flat screen TV 
- Wifi (Internet)
- Sofa & Table 
- Refrigerator
- Basic kitchen amenities ( refer kitchen photos to know more about kitchen utensils provided ) 
- Hot water (Geyser)
- Daily Housekeeping

In this space we provide an entire 1 BHK flat, it has a living room with comfortable sofa and a table to sit and watch TV or browse through internet on WiFi, and in kitchen there is basic amenities like Induction stove to cook, kettle for hot water, refrigerator to stock up your beverages, oven to heat food, and also cooker, pans ,pots and milk pan plates,glasses,cups and spoons. There is a bedroom with king size bed and comfortable and soft Sleepwell mattress for a relaxing sleep with Air conditioner as well, bathroom has a shower and geyser for hot water , we provide towels, soaps, toilet paper and hand wash.

Apart from the stay, property is at a good and safe neighborhood with everything you need at just walkable distance like Restaurants, Banks & ATM'S, supermarkets, pubs, hospitals, parks, and good public transportation facilities as well.
Building has a CCTV surveillance for your safety 24/7, and a parking space for two wheeler/Car.

Guest will have access to whole building ( staircase, terrace, parking space, common areas )

I respect guests privacy but i'll be available by phone calls and texts, I can communicate and guide regarding anything about the stay, house manual, nearby location tips, best places to eat, or any other requirement I'll be more than happy to help you with it.

Our stay is located in JP Nagar, Bangalore, it is an amazing place surrounded by various hangout places and restaurants of all cuisines are available, Bangalore's largest malls like royal Meenakshi mall, vega city mall, Gopalan mall, and central mall are just 10-15mins away from our stay, Hospitals and medical shops are just walkable distance, all major Banks and ATM's are located within 500 meters, it is an ideal location for everything you need in a city.

There are Various Public transports like  Buses, Metro stations, Autos, Cabs.

If you need more details about transportation facilities and how to get around in the city or the area of stay, I'd be sharing you all the details through a message or call depending upon your requirement.

NOTE: 

We don't have Room service or a caretaker at the property, so if you need anything you need to step out to get it by yourself or if you don't want to step out at all doorstep deliveries options are available to the property like swiggy, zomato, dunzo, big basket, etc.

description:
Welcome,Gloss over the stay details below

Type of stay ( ENTIRE 1 BHK)
- 1 BHK Apartment with living room, kitchen, Bedroom with attached bathroom

Amenities 
- king size bed
- comfortable sleepwell mattress
- Essentials ( Towels, soaps, Handwash, toilet paper, extra blankets)
- Air Conditioner
- Flat screen TV 
- WiFi(internet)
- Sofa & Table 
- Refrigerator
- Basic kitchen utensils ( Refer kitchen photos for more details)
- Daily Housekeeping
- Washing Machine ( Additional charge)

In this space we provide an entire 1 BHK flat, it has a living room with comfortable sofa and a table to sit and watch TV or browse through internet on WiFi, and in kitchen there is basic amenities like kettle for hot water, refrigerator to stock up your beverages, oven to heat food, Induction stove to cook with cooker, pots, pan, milk pan and kadai and also plates,glasses,cups and spoons, there is a bedroom with king size bed and comfortable and soft Sleepwell mattress for a relaxing sleep with Air conditioner as well, bathroom has a shower and geyser for hot water , we provide towels, soaps, toilet paper and hand wash.

Apart from the stay, property is at a good and safe neighborhood safe for families,couples,kids, friends,solo and women travellers with everything you need at just walkable distance like Restaurants, Banks & ATM'S, supermarkets, pubs, hospitals, parks, and good public transportation facilities as well
Building has a CCTV surveillance for your safety 24/7, and a parking space for two wheeler/Car.

Guest will have access to whole building ( staircase, terrace, parking space, common areas )

I respect guests privacy but i'll be available by phone calls and texts, I can communicate and guide regarding anything about the stay, house manual, nearby location tips, best places to eat, or any other requirement I'll be more than happy to help you with it.

Our stay is located in JP Nagar, Bangalore, it is an amazing place surrounded by various hangout places and restaurants of all cuisines are available, Bangalore's largest malls like royal Meenakshi mall, vega city mall, Gopalan mall, and central mall are just 10-15mins away from our stay, Hospitals and medical shops are just walkable distance, all major Banks and ATM's are located within 500 meters, it is an ideal location for everything you need in a city.

There are Various Public transports like  Buses, Metro stations, Autos, Cabs.

If you need more details about transportation facilities and how to get around in the city or the area of stay, I'd be sharing you all the details through a message or call depending upon your requirement.

NOTE: 

We don't have Room service or a caretaker at the property, so if you need anything you need to step out to get it by yourself or if you don't want to step out all doorstep deliveries options are available to the property like swiggy, zomato, dunzo, big basket etc.

summary: A great space for two or three travellers in the middle of the city, with a beautiful garden terrace overlooking the army cantonment. Close to all IT and manufacturing hubs in Bengaluru, and even closer to the top party destinations of the city. Well lit and decorated ambience welcomes you as you check in. amenities: Cable TV,Dryer,Ethernet connection,Essentials,Hot water,Iron,Laptop-friendly workspace,TV,Washer,Wifi,Free street parking,Coffee maker,Cooking basics,Dishes and silverware,Kitchen,Microwave,Refrigerator,Stove,Building staff,Private entrance,Long term stays allowed,Bed linens,Extra pillows and blankets,Hangers,Shampoo,Patio or balcony,Garden or backyard,Lake access,Waterfront,Fire extinguisher,Carbon monoxide alarm,Smoke alarm,First aid kit
description:
A great space for two or three travellers in the middle of the city, with a beautiful garden terrace overlooking the army cantonment. Close to all IT and manufacturing hubs in Bengaluru, and even closer to the top party destinations of the city. Well lit and decorated ambience welcomes you as you check in. All conveniences available nearby, including hospitals, malls, restaurants and departmental stores.Accommodating host presents this space on the third floor of their home, and is pet friendly

Food available from hundreds of restaurants via telephone. Parking space available. CCTV monitored in a quiet and secure neighbourhood. Well known Tree Park within walking distance. Bangalore's biggest lake lies within a distance of 1 KM. Great for morning walks.

Microwave, cooking facilities, utensils, TV, bedroom, bathroom, balcony, terrace, parking, wash area, laundry on request, bicycle on request

Friendly and brief

Upscale neighbourhood of Koramangala 3rd block, known for it parks, public gardens, lakes, nightlife, and gastronomic excursions waits for you.

Auto, cabs, cycle, rental 2 wheelers and 4 wheelers & plentiful public transport.

Please read the tips displayed inside the property for comfortable and safe stay. We allow flexible check-in mostly after the standard check in time, but have a place to drop off the luggage and to wait in a common area for early check-in. Check out time is 10 AM. No loud music.

additional_house_rules:
Check out time is 10.00 AM.
Use of washing machine is on a payable basis at Rs. 200 for a load upto 5 kgs.

Loud music and parties not allowed.

The place is residential so expected to be quiet.

Only no.of booked guests are allowed. Any additional guest will be accommodated as per the charges listed. Prior information mandatory for visiting guests.

Events or parties to be communicated well in advance.

description:
New apartment house on the top floor well maintained and decorated with modern amenities  in a very convenient & prime location. We have a beautiful kitchen  and have beautiful views of BloreCity from the apartment .Close to Global Village Tech park , Metro Station, markets, restaurants , BGS hospital just 1-2 km).Can each any part of the city by Metro.
Fully furnished apartment including power backup / washer dryer / Stocked up. As it’s long term , there would be additional Rs 3000 maintenance

This is a 3bhk flat with guest access upto 2 bedrooms with required essentials like double bed ,geyser , kitchen , sofa and wardrobe ,TV  .The views from the apartment are great since its on the 6th floor.Its also a newly constructed apartment , hence its very cosy and clean.
additional_house_rules: This is a strict vegetarian house and you are not supposed to cook Non-Vegetarian !

description:
This beautiful home away from home is located right next to JUST TRUFFS CHOCOLATIERS.

1km interior from the new international airport road.

Situated in one of the Bangalore's most amazing residential layouts (BGS). Placed on the 2nd floor of a independent house with ample parking space and privacy.

Very good access to cabs towards the city as well as the airport.

On call attendant for any queries and assistance.

This home is a newly built area considering the safely, privacy and vastu.

Our space has attached washroom for both the rooms, we have a maid who visits everyday for cleaning it by afternoon. 

There is a full time bell boy and security to take care of the guests safety. Provided with unlimited wifi, Tata sky and kitchen utensils which can be used for entertainment and cooking respectively. Geezer has been attached to one of the bathrooms and also solar water will be provided through out the day.
A private balcony for outdoor relaxation since our layout is blessed with ample trees and greenery.

Iron box, washing machine, microwave , RO water filter from Livpure has been also included in the tariff.

Have a pleasant stay. :)

Available to contact us by email, text or phone.

Peaceful neighbors since it's a independent house and no one to interfere our privacy.

Car parking is available

Since it's just 1km away from new airport( Ballary main road), taxi from the airport takes 30mins to reach, 13kms from the mejastic railways and bus stand. 10 mins drive from manyata tech park.

Kindly use water and power as per the requirements. Wastage of any of these  unnecessarily is definitely a natural loss.
neighborhood_overview: Peaceful neighbors since it's a independent house and no one to interfere our privacy.

name: Garnet Suite - A Self-Serviced Residence, Hebbal
summary:
This 2BHK residence is situated on the 1st floor in a quiet residential neighbourhood. The residence has a fully functional kitchen.
The residence close to the new airport, Cantonment and Yeshwantpur Railway Station.
The space is also well connected to the popular areas of Bangalore such as MG Road and Commercial Street. World Trade Centre,  Manyata Tech Park, or Brigade Magnum.
The closest bus-stop is a 5 mins walk from the space. We offer great discounts for long stays
amenities: Air conditioning,Dryer,Essentials,Hot water,Iron,Laptop-friendly workspace,Pocket wifi,TV,Washer,Wifi,Game console,Pack ’n Play/travel crib,Window guards,Elevator,Free parking on premises,Single level home,Free street parking,Cooking basics,Dishes and silverware,Kitchen,Microwave,Refrigerator,Stove,Private entrance,Smart lock,Cleaning before checkout,Luggage dropoff allowed,Long term stays allowed,Bed linens,Extra pillows and blankets,Hair dryer,Hangers,Shampoo,Shower gel,First aid kit
description:
This 2BHK residence is situated on the 1st floor in a quiet residential neighbourhood. The residence has a fully functional kitchen.
The residence close to the new airport, Cantonment and Yeshwantpur Railway Station.
The space is also well connected to the popular areas of Bangalore such as MG Road and Commercial Street. World Trade Centre,  Manyata Tech Park, or Brigade Magnum.
The closest bus-stop is a 5 mins walk from the space. We offer great discounts for long stays

This residence is Luxurious, cozy, comfortable with large windows that fill the house with natural daylight.
There are plenty of restaurants and stores just walking distance away that makes this a perfect location. 
The residence also has a fully functional kitchen complete with an induction stove, microwave oven, cutlery and crockery.
If you are a foodie then the famous RT Nagar 80 feet road is just walking distance away and BEL road is 2 kms away which gives you access to a variety of watering holes and popular restaurants.
The residence is around 45 mins away from the airport and 20 mins away from both Yeshwanthpur and Cantonment Railway stations.

The Residence comes with :-

* Hi Speed Wifi 
* 40 Inch Flat screen TV with Amazon Fire Stick - Stream Netflix , Amazon Prime , Hotstar or YouTube straight from your device to the TV.
* Air-conditioned - Both the bedrooms in the house are Air-conditioned.
* UPS Power back-up
* RO Water Purifier.
* Fully functional Kitchen with Cutlery, Crockery and Utensils 
* Laundry - Washing Machine (Detergent Available on MRP)
* Housekeeping, toiletries, linen and towels are included.
* Cornflakes, Maggie Noodles, Milk Powder, Coffee and Tea is available.
* We can also stock the fridge or kitchen for you on request.
* Car parking - We have a secured car parking space in the building.
* We have bike rentals on demand.
* We can also provide you transfers to and from the Bangalore Airport.

What's Local 

1. There is RT Nagar 80 Feet Road a 5mins walk from the residence, which has popular restaurants like Kudla, Empire, Rahhams etc and fast food joints like KFC, Pizza Hut, McDonalds, you will be defiantly spoiled for choice with various cuisines to sample.
2. BEL road is 2Kms away which gives you access to a few more famous watering holes and resturants
3. The very popular " Hammered Exchange Bar" is just 3Kms away
4. There is a micro brewery called " The Druid Garden"( 4 kms from the space) if you love beer you can sample their local brews. If you love modern architecture their interiors are a must see.
5. If you love to dance there is a roof top bar called "Gravity" that faces the Nagawara lake (4 kms from the space), they have some excellent music on the weekends and a fabulous view of surrounding lake.
6. India's largest micro brewery "BYG Brewski" is 30 mins drive away, this 65,000 square feet microbrewery serves 16 types of beer on tap and is a must try.

You have access to the entire flat its more or less yours.

I live close by and I am just a phone call away if you need me to assist you with anything. 
I am a travel buff and a foodie and would love to spill the beans on local hang-outs and food joints.

The Space is located on in a gated apartment complex in a quiet residential neighbourhood.
The flat is directly connected to the new airport by an expressway which makes your commute a quick 30mins drive to and from the airport. 
Yeshwantpur and Cantonment  Railways stations are just a 20 min drive away.
The space is also well connected to the popular areas of Bangalore such as MG Road and Commercial Street. (by bus, rickshaw, Uber or Ola Cab’s)
If you have business at Brigade World Trade Centre, Manyata Tech Park or Brigade Magnum your just a 15 Mins Drive away.

Bangalore is well covered by UBER and OLA cabs, so getting around town is as easy as a push of a button.
The nearest bus-stop is a 5 mins walk away.
There is also a rickshaw stand very close-by.
We have bike rentals too.

This is a residential apartment complex so please me mindful of noise levels

additional_house_rules:
* Quiet Time 11pm.
* Please segregate your waste dustbins for wet and dry will be provided.
* No Dirty Dishes in the sink please. - If you require us to do the dishes please do let us know we can accommodate this request for an additional cleaning fee of Rs 300 for each request.
* Please ensure geysers and air-conditioners are switched off after use. Small steps will help save the environment.
* Housekeeping - Dusting & Mopping will be done very alternate day for stays less that 7 days and every week for stays longer than 7 days.
* Please restrict smoking in the bedrooms.
* We are restricted to only hosting married couples, families and single travellers, please do message me if you have any queries on this
* If you require us to stock up the kitchen or fridge do let us know and we shall be happy to help you out.

Our house is located in a peaceful neighborhood which is free from the city noise and pollution, this makes our neighborhood unique and special.

Our property is at a walkable distance to the bus stop in Mohammed Sab Palya. Uber and Ola cabs can be booked through app in mobile and will reach our place in no time.

Please follow the rules mentioned by us in Airbnb. Please ensure that you keep the house neat and clean as we don’t have a dedicated house keeping and we don’t charge extra for guests as cleaning charges.Washing machine should be used only in morning time and please don’t use after 10pm at night. Use only microwave safe vessels in the microwave oven provided.  An Umbrella, Bluetooth Speaker and First Aid Kit is kept in the Hall, Hair Dryer, 5 Bath Towels,  Extra Mattresses and Pillows are kept in Bedroom No. 1 Almirah for use. The plates kept on the stand and on top of the microwave oven are microwave safe. Please switch off the outside lights before going to bed every night and please close the gates when you get in and get out of the home. Everything in the house is accounted for before the guest arrives and after the guest leaves, so please DO NOT take anything from the house without our permission.

additional_house_rules:
- No Escorts

- Parties not allowed. 

-Drugs are strictly prohibited. 

- During check out, you're expected to leave the Homestay just the way you found it during checking in. 

- Do not use the property for engaging in illegal activities.

- Do not spit inside washbasin or anywhere inside the house after eating Tobacco products.

-Please leave your footwear outside home.

- There is an extra charge after 4th guest onwards. 5th to 8th guest will be charged extra. The charges would be automatically calculated in Airbnb. The guest has to put the no of guests while booking in Airbnb.Cctv's are installed outside the home to monitor and to know the total guests booked with us. Kindly be genuine and transparent while adding guests. We would not encourage guests who have not booked with us. 

- Quiet hours after 10pm. Do not use the washing machine from 10pm-04am. Please don't cause a nuisance in Neighborhood.

- A switch for switching on the outside light is given outside near automatic water controller device. 

-Govt Rules and Regulations: Guests are requested to observe Govt rules and regulations in force, in respect of registeration, alcoholic drinks, firearms etc. Form C should be filled in or handed over to the concerned Police station by Non Indians. 

- Please close the door when stepping out to garden or deck.

- Air conditioning is charged at an additional Rs.300/day if you need it. 

- Please ensure you clean the house and utensils if used as we don't have housekeeping services and also we don't charge extra money on account of cleaning charges.If housekeeping is required you can directly speak to her and fix the price for the day which includes brooming, moping and cleaning the utensils This can be paid directly to the housekeeper. 

- Garbage should be put in the garbage bags provided in the kitchen and placed inside the blue drum at the front of the house. 

- Please ensure that lights, fans and T.V are switched off when you leave the house. 

- We have marked the switches / plug sockets of the house to identify the purpose of use. Please try to use it only for those purposes. If there are any doubts regarding the same, I shall guide you accordingly.

- Wifi speed is 75 Mbps till 305 GB for a month, post that it will be 512 Kbps. 

- Please switch off all the outside lights before sleeping. 

- Please don't use the cushions of SOFA as headrest in bed. They are meant for Sofa only. Seperate pillows are kept in Almirah for use. 

- Please respect the serenity of the environment. 

- Kindly take care of all the things inside the house as your own.

- Umbrella is kept in the main hall and a hair dryer is kept in the bedroom for use. 

- Bluetooth speaker with charger is kept in the main hall. 

- 5 Towels are kept inside Almirah for use. 

- Garbage  plastic bags are kept in Kitchen wherein the guests have to segregate the dry and wet waste separately. Once the bag is filled you need to drop the waste with the bag to the Blue drum kept outside.

Enjoy the homely environment in midst of greener. close to colleges, malls, temples and other tourist attractions in south Bangalore. home food is available for breakfast, lunch and dinner with extra nominal charges

2 bedroom house with fully furnished amenities. host stays nearby, there are lot of trees around if you want to take a walk during evening or morning

guests will have access to terrace where they can sit and enjoy a coffee

as a host I will be a available over call or WhatsApp anytime and if needed I can drive to the place in 5 to 10 mins

lot of greenery,  schools, shops, temples and malls are nearby

you could ola or uber anytime. there are also rental bikes available. we will provide pick up and drop services with additional nominal charges

name: HelloWorld Lake View - 1BHK | BTM Layout | HSR -04
summary:
HelloWorld Lake View, where you’ll make your best memories in our beautiful Bangalore city. We’ve crafted a stay for you to experience a friendly & functional environment that goes the extra mile for you.

description:
HelloWorld Lake View, where you’ll make your best memories in our beautiful Bangalore city. We’ve crafted a stay for you to experience a friendly & functional environment that goes the extra mile for you.

It's a 1BHK fully furnished setup located in the heart of the city in BTM 2nd stage near Silk Board junction. BTM lake is 100 metres from our place. 

Nearby areas are HSR, Bellandur, Electronics City, Kormangala, Jayanagar, Tavarekere

It is a fully furnished 1BHK flat. Our rooms have been designed with the utmost attention to comfort & good vibes. Our building has an equipped kitchen where you can have a yummy breakfast, lunch, and dinner.

Our specially designed Rooftop where you can lounge on the couch and chill, or have a drink over fun conversation and great music.

Building Caretaker is always available at the building on the ground floor. He is very friendly. If in case he is not able to help you with anything you can contact me anytime.

It has a lot of food joints nearby and supermarkets on walk-able distance. BTM lake is at a 100-meter distance. A lot of pubs are there in around 2-3 km. Also, this property is situated center of the city with very well connected to major areas in Bengaluru like BTM, HSR, Silk Board, Koramangala, Electronics City, Indiranagar, Domlur.

It is very well connected with all kinds of transportations. Uber, Ola, Airport Taxi, Volvo Buses(1KM Radius) are easily accessible. Two Wheeler parking is available in the building.

description:
Welcome, Gloss over the stay details 
Type of stay ( ENTIRE 1 BHK)
- 1 BHK Apartment with living room, kitchen, Bedroom with attached bathroom.
Amenities 
- king size bed
- comfortable Sleepwell mattress
- Essentials ( Towels, soaps, Handwash, toilet paper, extra blankets)
- Air Conditioner
- Flat screen TV 
- Wifi (Internet)
- Sofa & Table 
- Refrigerator
- Basic kitchen amenities ( refer kitchen photos to know more about kitchen utensils provided ) 
- Hot water (Geyser)
- Daily Housekeeping

In this space we provide an entire 1 BHK flat, it has a living room with comfortable sofa and a table to sit and watch TV or browse through internet on WiFi, and in kitchen there is basic amenities like Induction stove to cook, kettle for hot water, refrigerator to stock up your beverages, oven to heat food, and also cooker, pans ,pots and milk pan plates,glasses,cups and spoons. There is a bedroom with king size bed and comfortable and soft Sleepwell mattress for a relaxing sleep with Air conditioner as well, bathroom has a shower and geyser for hot water , we provide towels, soaps, toilet paper and hand wash.

Apart from the stay, property is at a good and safe neighborhood with everything you need at just walkable distance like Restaurants, Banks & ATM'S, supermarkets, pubs, hospitals, parks, and good public transportation facilities as well.
Building has a CCTV surveillance for your safety 24/7, and a parking space for two wheeler/Car.

Guest will have access to whole building ( staircase, terrace, parking space, common areas )

I respect guests privacy but i'll be available by phone calls and texts, I can communicate and guide regarding anything about the stay, house manual, nearby location tips, best places to eat, or any other requirement I'll be more than happy to help you with it.

Our stay is located in JP Nagar, Bangalore, it is an amazing place surrounded by various hangout places and restaurants of all cuisines are available, Bangalore's largest malls like royal Meenakshi mall, vega city mall, Gopalan mall, and central mall are just 10-15mins away from our stay, Hospitals and medical shops are just walkable distance, all major Banks and ATM's are located within 500 meters, it is an ideal location for everything you need in a city.

There are Various Public transports like  Buses, Metro stations, Autos, Cabs.

If you need more details about transportation facilities and how to get around in the city or the area of stay, I'd be sharing you all the details through a message or call depending upon your requirement.

NOTE: 

We don't have Room service or a caretaker at the property, so if you need anything you need to step out to get it by yourself or if you don't want to step out at all doorstep deliveries options are available to the property like swiggy, zomato, dunzo, big basket, etc.

description:
Welcome,Gloss over the stay details below

Type of stay ( ENTIRE 1 BHK)
- 1 BHK Apartment with living room, kitchen, Bedroom with attached bathroom

Amenities 
- king size bed
- comfortable sleepwell mattress
- Essentials ( Towels, soaps, Handwash, toilet paper, extra blankets)
- Air Conditioner
- Flat screen TV 
- WiFi(internet)
- Sofa & Table 
- Refrigerator
- Basic kitchen utensils ( Refer kitchen photos for more details)
- Daily Housekeeping
- Washing Machine ( Additional charge)

In this space we provide an entire 1 BHK flat, it has a living room with comfortable sofa and a table to sit and watch TV or browse through internet on WiFi, and in kitchen there is basic amenities like kettle for hot water, refrigerator to stock up your beverages, oven to heat food, Induction stove to cook with cooker, pots, pan, milk pan and kadai and also plates,glasses,cups and spoons, there is a bedroom with king size bed and comfortable and soft Sleepwell mattress for a relaxing sleep with Air conditioner as well, bathroom has a shower and geyser for hot water , we provide towels, soaps, toilet paper and hand wash.

Apart from the stay, property is at a good and safe neighborhood safe for families,couples,kids, friends,solo and women travellers with everything you need at just walkable distance like Restaurants, Banks & ATM'S, supermarkets, pubs, hospitals, parks, and good public transportation facilities as well
Building has a CCTV surveillance for your safety 24/7, and a parking space for two wheeler/Car.

Guest will have access to whole building ( staircase, terrace, parking space, common areas )

I respect guests privacy but i'll be available by phone calls and texts, I can communicate and guide regarding anything about the stay, house manual, nearby location tips, best places to eat, or any other requirement I'll be more than happy to help you with it.

Our stay is located in JP Nagar, Bangalore, it is an amazing place surrounded by various hangout places and restaurants of all cuisines are available, Bangalore's largest malls like royal Meenakshi mall, vega city mall, Gopalan mall, and central mall are just 10-15mins away from our stay, Hospitals and medical shops are just walkable distance, all major Banks and ATM's are located within 500 meters, it is an ideal location for everything you need in a city.

There are Various Public transports like  Buses, Metro stations, Autos, Cabs.

If you need more details about transportation facilities and how to get around in the city or the area of stay, I'd be sharing you all the details through a message or call depending upon your requirement.

NOTE: 

We don't have Room service or a caretaker at the property, so if you need anything you need to step out to get it by yourself or if you don't want to step out all doorstep deliveries options are available to the property like swiggy, zomato, dunzo, big basket etc.

summary: A great space for two or three travellers in the middle of the city, with a beautiful garden terrace overlooking the army cantonment. Close to all IT and manufacturing hubs in Bengaluru, and even closer to the top party destinations of the city. Well lit and decorated ambience welcomes you as you check in. All conveniences available nearby, including hospitals, malls, restaurants and departmental stores.Accommodating host presents this space on the third floor of their home, and is pet friendly
amenities: Cable TV,Dryer,Ethernet connection,Essentials,Hot water,Iron,Laptop-friendly workspace,TV,Washer,Wifi,Free street parking,Coffee maker,Cooking basics,Dishes and silverware,Kitchen,Microwave,Refrigerator,Stove,Building staff,Private entrance,Long term stays allowed,Bed linens,Extra pillows and blankets,Hangers,Shampoo,Patio or balcony,Garden or backyard,Lake access,Waterfront,Fire extinguisher,Carbon monoxide alarm,Smoke alarm,First aid kit
description:
A great space for two or three travellers in the middle of the city, with a beautiful garden terrace overlooking the army cantonment. Close to all IT and manufacturing hubs in Bengaluru, and even closer to the top party destinations of the city. Well lit and decorated ambience welcomes you as you check in. All conveniences available nearby, including hospitals, malls, restaurants and departmental stores.Accommodating host presents this space on the third floor of their home, and is pet friendly

Food available from hundreds of restaurants via telephone. Parking space available. CCTV monitored in a quiet and secure neighbourhood. Well known Tree Park within walking distance. Bangalore's biggest lake lies within a distance of 1 KM. Great for morning walks.

Microwave, cooking facilities, utensils, TV, bedroom, bathroom, balcony, terrace, parking, wash area, laundry on request, bicycle on request

Friendly and brief

Upscale neighbourhood of Koramangala 3rd block, known for it parks, public gardens, lakes, nightlife, and gastronomic excursions waits for you.

Auto, cabs, cycle, rental 2 wheelers and 4 wheelers & plentiful public transport.

Please read the tips displayed inside the property for comfortable and safe stay. We allow flexible check-in mostly after the standard check in time, but have a place to drop off the luggage and to wait in a common area for early check-in. Check out time is 10 AM. No loud music.

additional_house_rules:
Check out time is 10.00 AM.
Use of washing machine is on a payable basis at Rs. 200 for a load upto 5 kgs.

Loud music and parties not allowed.

The place is residential so expected to be quiet.

Only no.of booked guests are allowed. Any additional guest will be accommodated as per the charges listed. Prior information mandatory for visiting guests.

Events or parties to be communicated well in advance.

New apartment house on the top floor well maintained and decorated with modern amenities  in a very convenient & prime location. We have a beautiful kitchen  and have beautiful views of BloreCity from the apartment .Close to Global Village Tech park , Metro Station, markets, restaurants , BGS hospital just 1-2 km).Can each any part of the city by Metro.

This is a 3bhk flat with guest access upto 2 bedrooms with required essentials like double bed ,geyser , kitchen , sofa and wardrobe ,TV  .The views from the apartment are great since its on the 6th floor.Its also a newly constructed apartment , hence its very cosy and clean.

description:
This beautiful home away from home is located right next to JUST TRUFFS CHOCOLATIERS.

1km interior from the new international airport road.

Situated in one of the Bangalore's most amazing residential layouts (BGS). Placed on the 2nd floor of a independent house with ample parking space and privacy.

Very good access to cabs towards the city as well as the airport.

On call attendant for any queries and assistance.

This home is a newly built area considering the safely, privacy and vastu.

Our space has attached washroom for both the rooms, we have a maid who visits everyday for cleaning it by afternoon. 

There is a full time bell boy and security to take care of the guests safety. Provided with unlimited wifi, Tata sky and kitchen utensils which can be used for entertainment and cooking respectively. Geezer has been attached to one of the bathrooms and also solar water will be provided through out the day.
A private balcony for outdoor relaxation since our layout is blessed with ample trees and greenery.

Iron box, washing machine, microwave , RO water filter from Livpure has been also included in the tariff.

Have a pleasant stay. :)

Available to contact us by email, text or phone.

Peaceful neighbors since it's a independent house and no one to interfere our privacy.

Car parking is available

Since it's just 1km away from new airport( Ballary main road), taxi from the airport takes 30mins to reach, 13kms from the mejastic railways and bus stand. 10 mins drive from manyata tech park.

Kindly use water and power as per the requirements. Wastage of any of these  unnecessarily is definitely a natural loss.
neighborhood_overview: Peaceful neighbors since it's a independent house and no one to interfere our privacy.

summary:
My place is close to Bangalore's city centre. 
You’ll love my place because of the location, the people, the hosts of-course, the privacy with separate entrance through the Garden, the ambience, and the quite neighbourhood and the dedicate service that we provide. 
My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, business travellers, extended stay guests, relocation's, corporate guests and guests with self cooking needs.

name: Garnet Suite - A Self-Serviced Residence, Hebbal
summary:
This 2BHK residence is situated on the 1st floor in a quiet residential neighbourhood. The residence has a fully functional kitchen.
The residence close to the new airport, Cantonment and Yeshwantpur Railway Station.
The space is also well connected to the popular areas of Bangalore such as MG Road and Commercial Street. World Trade Centre,  Manyata Tech Park, or Brigade Magnum.
The closest bus-stop is a 5 mins walk from the space. We offer great discounts for long stays

description:
This 2BHK residence is situated on the 1st floor in a quiet residential neighbourhood. The residence has a fully functional kitchen.
The residence close to the new airport, Cantonment and Yeshwantpur Railway Station.
The space is also well connected to the popular areas of Bangalore such as MG Road and Commercial Street. World Trade Centre,  Manyata Tech Park, or Brigade Magnum.
The closest bus-stop is a 5 mins walk from the space. We offer great discounts for long stays

This residence is Luxurious, cozy, comfortable with large windows that fill the house with natural daylight.
There are plenty of restaurants and stores just walking distance away that makes this a perfect location. 
The residence also has a fully functional kitchen complete with an induction stove, microwave oven, cutlery and crockery.
If you are a foodie then the famous RT Nagar 80 feet road is just walking distance away and BEL road is 2 kms away which gives you access to a variety of watering holes and popular restaurants.
The residence is around 45 mins away from the airport and 20 mins away from both Yeshwanthpur and Cantonment Railway stations.

The Residence comes with :-

* Hi Speed Wifi 
* 40 Inch Flat screen TV with Amazon Fire Stick - Stream Netflix , Amazon Prime , Hotstar or YouTube straight from your device to the TV.
* Air-conditioned - Both the bedrooms in the house are Air-conditioned.
* UPS Power back-up
* RO Water Purifier.
* Fully functional Kitchen with Cutlery, Crockery and Utensils 
* Laundry - Washing Machine (Detergent Available on MRP)
* Housekeeping, toiletries, linen and towels are included.
* Cornflakes, Maggie Noodles, Milk Powder, Coffee and Tea is available.
* We can also stock the fridge or kitchen for you on request.
* Car parking - We have a secured car parking space in the building.
* We have bike rentals on demand.
* We can also provide you transfers to and from the Bangalore Airport.

What's Local 

1. There is RT Nagar 80 Feet Road a 5mins walk from the residence, which has popular restaurants like Kudla, Empire, Rahhams etc and fast food joints like KFC, Pizza Hut, McDonalds, you will be defiantly spoiled for choice with various cuisines to sample.
2. BEL road is 2Kms away which gives you access to a few more famous watering holes and resturants
3. The very popular " Hammered Exchange Bar" is just 3Kms away
4. There is a micro brewery called " The Druid Garden"( 4 kms from the space) if you love beer you can sample their local brews. If you love modern architecture their interiors are a must see.
5. If you love to dance there is a roof top bar called "Gravity" that faces the Nagawara lake (4 kms from the space), they have some excellent music on the weekends and a fabulous view of surrounding lake.
6. India's largest micro brewery "BYG Brewski" is 30 mins drive away, this 65,000 square feet microbrewery serves 16 types of beer on tap and is a must try.

You have access to the entire flat its more or less yours.

I live close by and I am just a phone call away if you need me to assist you with anything. 
I am a travel buff and a foodie and would love to spill the beans on local hang-outs and food joints.

The Space is located on in a gated apartment complex in a quiet residential neighbourhood.
The flat is directly connected to the new airport by an expressway which makes your commute a quick 30mins drive to and from the airport. 
Yeshwantpur and Cantonment  Railways stations are just a 20 min drive away.
The space is also well connected to the popular areas of Bangalore such as MG Road and Commercial Street. (by bus, rickshaw, Uber or Ola Cab’s)
If you have business at Brigade World Trade Centre, Manyata Tech Park or Brigade Magnum your just a 15 Mins Drive away.

Bangalore is well covered by UBER and OLA cabs, so getting around town is as easy as a push of a button.
The nearest bus-stop is a 5 mins walk away.
There is also a rickshaw stand very close-by.
We have bike rentals too.

This is a residential apartment complex so please me mindful of noise levels

additional_house_rules:
* Quiet Time 11pm.
* Please segregate your waste dustbins for wet and dry will be provided.
* No Dirty Dishes in the sink please. - If you require us to do the dishes please do let us know we can accommodate this request for an additional cleaning fee of Rs 300 for each request.
* Please ensure geysers and air-conditioners are switched off after use. Small steps will help save the environment.
* Housekeeping - Dusting & Mopping will be done very alternate day for stays less that 7 days and every week for stays longer than 7 days.
* Please restrict smoking in the bedrooms.
* We are restricted to only hosting married couples, families and single travellers, please do message me if you have any queries on this
* If you require us to stock up the kitchen or fridge do let us know and we shall be happy to help you out.

This house is in the ground floor and is fully furnished 2 bedroom house which comes with A.C,Wifi,T.V,Solar Water heater,Water Purifier,5 beds +3 floor Mattresses,Dining Table,Shower Gel, Shampoo,Towels,Ironing table with Iron, Kitchen with Utensils,LPG connection with Stove,Microwave Oven,Washing Machine and Fridge. You will find everything you need like restaurants, supermarkets, groceries, hospitals, schools, colleges, ATMs, petrol pumps etc in close vicinity.

Our house is located in a peaceful neighborhood which is free from the city noise and pollution, this makes our neighborhood unique and special.

Our property is at a walkable distance to the bus stop in Mohammed Sab Palya. Uber and Ola cabs can be booked through app in mobile and will reach our place in no time.

Please follow the rules mentioned by us in Airbnb. Please ensure that you keep the house neat and clean as we don’t have a dedicated house keeping and we don’t charge extra for guests as cleaning charges.Washing machine should be used only in morning time and please don’t use after 10pm at night. Use only microwave safe vessels in the microwave oven provided.  An Umbrella, Bluetooth Speaker and First Aid Kit is kept in the Hall, Hair Dryer, 5 Bath Towels,  Extra Mattresses and Pillows are kept in Bedroom No. 1 Almirah for use. The plates kept on the stand and on top of the microwave oven are microwave safe. Please switch off the outside lights before going to bed every night and please close the gates when you get in and get out of the home. Everything in the house is accounted for before the guest arrives and after the guest leaves, so please DO NOT take anything from the house without our permission.

additional_house_rules:
- No Escorts

- Parties not allowed. 

-Drugs are strictly prohibited. 

- During check out, you're expected to leave the Homestay just the way you found it during checking in. 

- Do not use the property for engaging in illegal activities.

- Do not spit inside washbasin or anywhere inside the house after eating Tobacco products.

-Please leave your footwear outside home.

- There is an extra charge after 4th guest onwards. 5th to 8th guest will be charged extra. The charges would be automatically calculated in Airbnb. The guest has to put the no of guests while booking in Airbnb.Cctv's are installed outside the home to monitor and to know the total guests booked with us. Kindly be genuine and transparent while adding guests. We would not encourage guests who have not booked with us. 

- Quiet hours after 10pm. Do not use the washing machine from 10pm-04am. Please don't cause a nuisance in Neighborhood.

- A switch for switching on the outside light is given outside near automatic water controller device. 

-Govt Rules and Regulations: Guests are requested to observe Govt rules and regulations in force, in respect of registeration, alcoholic drinks, firearms etc. Form C should be filled in or handed over to the concerned Police station by Non Indians. 

- Please close the door when stepping out to garden or deck.

- Air conditioning is charged at an additional Rs.300/day if you need it. 

- Please ensure you clean the house and utensils if used as we don't have housekeeping services and also we don't charge extra money on account of cleaning charges.If housekeeping is required you can directly speak to her and fix the price for the day which includes brooming, moping and cleaning the utensils This can be paid directly to the housekeeper. 

- Garbage should be put in the garbage bags provided in the kitchen and placed inside the blue drum at the front of the house. 

- Please ensure that lights, fans and T.V are switched off when you leave the house. 

- We have marked the switches / plug sockets of the house to identify the purpose of use. Please try to use it only for those purposes. If there are any doubts regarding the same, I shall guide you accordingly.

- Wifi speed is 75 Mbps till 305 GB for a month, post that it will be 512 Kbps. 

- Please switch off all the outside lights before sleeping. 

- Please don't use the cushions of SOFA as headrest in bed. They are meant for Sofa only. Seperate pillows are kept in Almirah for use. 

- Please respect the serenity of the environment. 

- Kindly take care of all the things inside the house as your own.

- Umbrella is kept in the main hall and a hair dryer is kept in the bedroom for use. 

- Bluetooth speaker with charger is kept in the main hall. 

- 5 Towels are kept inside Almirah for use. 

- Garbage  plastic bags are kept in Kitchen wherein the guests have to segregate the dry and wet waste separately. Once the bag is filled you need to drop the waste with the bag to the Blue drum kept outside.

description:
Enjoy the homely environment in midst of greener. close to colleges, malls, temples and other tourist attractions in south Bangalore. home food is available for breakfast, lunch and dinner with extra nominal charges

2 bedroom house with fully furnished amenities. host stays nearby, there are lot of trees around if you want to take a walk during evening or morning

guests will have access to terrace where they can sit and enjoy a coffee

as a host I will be a available over call or WhatsApp anytime and if needed I can drive to the place in 5 to 10 mins

lot of greenery,  schools, shops, temples and malls are nearby

you could ola or uber anytime. there are also rental bikes available. we will provide pick up and drop services with additional nominal charges
